                     <interp inst="t18520202-247-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>, stealing 9 shirts, and other articles, value 3<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; in a vessel in a port: to which</rs>
